## Typography

### Font Hierarchy
- **Headings**: Bold, impactful (consider display fonts)
- **Body**: Clean, readable sans-serif
- **Accents**: Slightly playful for Asterix theme elements

### Text Colors
```css
/* Light mode */
--text-primary: #1a1a1d;
--text-secondary: #455A64;
--text-accent: #00997d;

/* Dark mode */
--text-primary: #f4f4f9;
--text-secondary: #9ca3af;
--text-accent: #00997d;
```

## Component Styling Patterns

### Buttons
```tsx
// Primary (Village action)
<Button className="bg-emerald-600 hover:bg-emerald-700 text-white">
  Join the Resistance
</Button>

// Danger (Empire warning)
<Button variant="destructive" className="bg-red-700">
  Big Tech Trap
</Button>

// Magic Potion (special CTA)
<Button className="bg-amber-500 hover:bg-amber-600 text-black">
  Get the Potion
</Button>
```

### Cards
```tsx
// Village card (positive)
<Card className="border-emerald-200 bg-parchment">
  <CardContent>...</CardContent>
</Card>

// Empire card (warning)
<Card className="border-red-200 bg-red-50">
  <CardContent>...</CardContent>
</Card>
```

## Spacing & Layout

- Use consistent spacing: 4, 8, 12, 16, 24, 32, 48, 64, 96px
- Mobile-first responsive design
- Section padding: `py-16 md:py-24 lg:py-32`
- Container max-width: `max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4`

## Animation Guidelines

- Entrance animations: `duration-500` to `duration-700`
- Micro-interactions: `duration-200` to `duration-300`
- Scroll reveals: Stagger children by 100-150ms
- Easing: Use `ease-out` for entrances, `ease-in-out` for transitions

## Accessibility

- Maintain WCAG 2.1 AA contrast ratios
- Emerald on white: 4.5:1 ✓
- Gold on dark: Use darker shade for text
- Always provide focus states
- Support reduced-motion preferences
